===Verb===
'''X [[circles]] [[around]] (somebody)'''

#(''formulaic'') {{idiom}} To do X far faster or better than somebody else.
#:''You may think you're a fast typist, but he'll '''type circles around you''' any day!''

===Usage note===
This is a formulaic set phrase.  X may be replaced with nearly any verb.